snippet.title: PV (Full Version) - Space Leaper Reboot
snippet.description:
Get ready for the Action Packed Adventure Across the Unknown Cyber-Verse. Space Leaper: Cocoon, Strategy-Based Auto-Battler, is officially revealed!
In the year 3230, a cosmic explosion has sundered the universe and society has collapsed. Join the survivors aboard the Cocoon and piece together the Galaxy!

#SpaceLeaper
